Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:33.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:37.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:43.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一筋の光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:47.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:52.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷い　歩くすべを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:05.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:18.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:23.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今も微かな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:28.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう　未来と過去が交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}百年目の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:33.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一切都始於這靜靜燃燒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:37.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在長夜將明之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:43.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一道光芒 一聲發自靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:47.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}衝破束縛 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:52.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}尋求著歸宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷茫地邁足前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:05.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}這顆被波濤掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}甚至沒辦法保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}就像要跳出來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:18.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}留下無法忘卻的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:23.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}希望這微弱的殘影 永遠不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:28.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界正在等待 屬於明日的嬰啼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}千萬不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}是的 這是一首交錯著過去與未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}百年長歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑那麼快會跌倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 姊姊 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.65,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢點 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}橫須賀很久以前也像這裡一樣有一大片陸地吧 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 你大概已經學過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日俄戰爭之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隨著可燃冰的開採 日本的陸地開始沉降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們在被淹沒的城市上建造了巨型浮舟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形成了浮舟都市 繼續開發海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後日本就成了個海洋大國對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說大部分軍用船被改造成了民用船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過為了表示和平的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女性逐漸變成了艦長的首選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是藍色人魚的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧 真霜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一位女性艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是你們的曾祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之後 宗谷家的女人們都會成為藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過下次就是我最後一次出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後 我就是個培育藍色人魚的老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要培育胸懷世界 英姿颯爽 與海同生的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像這片廣袤的大海一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想成為那樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽去哪當老師我就去哪做學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要跟著媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回想起來 從那時開始我就一直不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厄運總是常伴我的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果這趟初次出航也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好慘 後方甲板看來得緊急修理一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有我們忙的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一萬個帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小美現在的眼裡只有野間同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等松同學 你有空的話倒是來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想把和真知知一起拍的照片發給妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但現在又不准用手機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小萌 小百 小美 你們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受損情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如你所見 需要緊急修理 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了 我等一下會過來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長還真忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小侖 你這邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都因為剛才的全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在得徹底檢修一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也太高估我們的發動機了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別叫得那麼親密 就不能叫我「黑木同學」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本就沒理你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是我們的艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小光 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小奈 小空 你們沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經記住我們名字了？厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是艦長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有其他傷員了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過事情變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴天霹靂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後要怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「知者不惑 仁者不憂 勇者不懼」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 請您立即返回艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受損情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}後方甲板被炸開一大塊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}深水炸彈還剩一枚 魚雷已經用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機室那邊還需要徹底檢修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別拍那種東西了 快點記錄受損情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校那邊有什麼消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該不會是把我們拋棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許他們正在確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我們只要撤退到鳥島附近洋面10海浬處就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 雖然那邊說我們發動了叛亂 還擊沉了猿島號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們必須解釋清楚才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會不會剛到集合地點就把我們抓起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們為什麼會攻擊猿島號？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是這樣的 是猿島號先開炮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的意思是他們不會相信我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們並沒有叛亂的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正漂在海上早晚會被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不如趕快就近靠港 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}入港之後應該也不至於再打我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鈴 回橫須賀大概要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用巡航速度大概要38小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 進了垃圾班還要受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼叫「垃圾班」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說會被分配來晴風號的 的確都是些成績墊底的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你自己不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是呢 我入學考試時本來應該是滿分的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果答題的時候錯開了一欄 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您真是不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 我這種人能考上已經很神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛好考了我複習過的地方 居然還讓我做了艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊這位就是個幸運兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種時候 要是能像那樣飛回學校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有沒有那種不用充氫氣或者氦氣就能飛的飛船？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼科幻的東西怎麼可能會有 真是無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位同學 吃飯的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是「晴風咖哩」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為今天是星期五嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們輪流去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們船上的咖哩不知道口味怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先洗澡 還是先吃咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先吃咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同學 我們一起去吃咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小黑你不和我一起怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右舷60度 距離30000 施佩伯爵號正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是德國留學生的船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先讓大家歸位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們以20節的航速靠近中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是被發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號 正在轉動主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們想開炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毫無交涉餘地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}野間同學 舉白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號 主炮開火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須把發動機也停下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只亮白旗的話確實說不上是投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們不是要逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 反轉航向180度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右滿舵 全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}著彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號也提速了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}壓迫上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號標準排水量12100噸 最大速度28.5節
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裝備6門28cm主炮 8門15cm副炮 8門魚雷發射管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最厚裝甲160mm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被稱為小型直教艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擁有巡洋艦水平的船體和直教艦水平的火炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}著彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主 主炮最大射程約為36000m
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能將重達300kg的炮彈以每分鐘2.5發的速度發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要中了一炮 我們就會被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說她們的15cm副炮其實就比我們的主炮要強了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們在火力和裝甲上占盡了優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有速度和靈活方面 我們能贏過她們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繼續馬力全開的話 發動機肯定會徹底壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發射魚雷爭取時間怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們有什麼炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}70 5
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射程7000m 穿深50mm？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號的舷側裝甲多厚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}80mm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}30
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距離縮短到30就能打穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們居然能正常對話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是天才式的艦長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小侖 穩定在什麼速度比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四戰速 也就是27節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和她們的最大戰速不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轉呀轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轉呀轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鈴 左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左 左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.21,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左轉30度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躲進煙霧裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回舵 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回舵 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右轉30度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被打中一次就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以必須活用速度和轉向能力 繞著彎逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小侖 讓燃料不完全燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冒煙擋住她們視線就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為要繞著彎逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發動機可能會承受很大壓力 總之拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但也只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鈴 隨機改變航向 可以的話航速也這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是儘量別減速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要想攔住他們只能開炮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷 炮戰準備 30度方向 目標施佩伯爵號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼呢 猿島號那件事以後你還不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用實彈打穿她們的艉軸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就能爭取時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再這樣下去就真的變成叛亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去的話 會有人受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啟用實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裝填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要打穿艉軸 得靠多近才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彈藥在入水時會突然減速的 辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是有那種水下彈藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}巡洋艦以上的級別才有 我們沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是普通彈藥 在水裡也是能前進的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}理論上來說12.7cm炮能在水裡前進10m
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果考慮到打穿舷側裝甲的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概得靠近到30以內才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保持8字型航路 把距離縮短到30
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要主動靠近嗎 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說了好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖乖靠近她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.57,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們嚴肅點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.90,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距離 40
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}38
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}36
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號放來了一艘小型船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小型船的船員落水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們在攻擊同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不願意聽從艦長的命令 為什麼要攻擊晴風號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 你敢違抗艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該死 這破船我才不稀罕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別在那妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我來說 虛構比非虛構更貼近現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.32,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直徑700m 角速度20節…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.98,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請叫我宗谷同學或者副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能把艦橋交給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}記得把德國船引過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸 叫醫務委員美波同學來甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要去救敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}海上的夥伴們都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長是去救那個落水的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把距離縮短到30
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距離32
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}31
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打啊打啊打個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二號炮台 右舷 開始炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號航速降低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左滿舵 第四戰速 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逃跑時她倒挺積極的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還好嗎 能聽見我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊的 你還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是下達了妥當的命令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最大戰速 立刻離開當前海域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小侖 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣會壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不能迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧 香香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美波同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她沒受外傷 腦波一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能等她自然醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來看著她 你去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一身臭汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於能清爽清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還以為發動機會壞掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 等了這麼久終於可以吃咖哩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是一萬個好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是「晴風咖哩」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於能吃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.57,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的飯是咖哩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.10,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是星期五嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.66,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對哦 今天星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說是甜咖哩但口感很醇厚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我們有放藍莓果醬來調味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來拿給真知知吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.80,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.68,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要叫「真知知」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}衛生委員長喜歡的是小黑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 宗谷同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 大概在艦橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同學 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我幫你拿咖哩來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別太勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有通訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 請立刻來艦橋一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}緊急通訊線路來電
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是武藏 這裡是武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香？我是明乃 你怎麼了 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們遇上了緊急狀況 請求立即救援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當前位置 亞松森島西北 亞松森島西北
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請求立即救援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請求立即救援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:24.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,480)}多災多難的反追擊戰！
Comment: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:25.07,Title,,0,0,0,,ED-FF
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:37.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:43.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:07.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:13.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:21.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:30.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:34.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:38.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:44.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:53.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:37.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我會比話語還要溫柔 輕輕地推著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:43.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是啊 這就是你和我之間的漣漪效應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}面前的驚濤駭浪 一浪捲來一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:07.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}我們選擇的航路 就是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:13.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}如果你忘記了微笑 我會笑給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:21.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}流過眼淚之後 讓堅強隨波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:30.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:34.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}比話語還要溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:38.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}是這片晴空和習習涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:44.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描繪夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}我希望我就是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:53.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}要相信春天正在等待著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:24:00.06,End,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.15\pos(1016,430)}下集也不容錯過哦{\i1}！{\i0}
